      For more travel advice, read the <a href="/the-guide/">Complete Brazil travel guide</a> and download the <a href="/free-starter-kit/">Free Brazil Starter Kit</a>. These resources include helpful tips on culture, safety, and planning.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

